"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Polygon在博客宣布将于北京时间今日16时（UTC时间12月14日上午8时）在Mumbai测试网启动EIP-1559升级，以引入其原生代币MATIC的燃烧机制和费用可预期性（fee visibility）。\\n\\n此前以太坊主网伦敦升级引入了EIP-1559改进提案，该提案更改以太坊主网Gas费用市场机制，引入代币的销毁机制。Polygon论坛上的一项研究认为，引入1559规则后，MATIC年度销毁量将占 MATIC 总供应量的 0.27%。（[Polygon](https://blog.polygon.technology/polygon-is-bringing-eip-1559-upgrades-to-its-network-with-a-testnet-release/?utm_source=Twitter-Main&utm_medium=Tweet&utm_campaign=Tier-1-Announcement)）\",\"timestamp\":1639993598,\"title\":\"Polygon计划今日在Mumbai测试网启动EIP-1559升级，引入Matic燃烧机制\"},\"digest\":\"-DmTK0TmcBfF8PuJeYA-sw0YQuW46pHJWj3VL6SYBYQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xe74a34fe4592c7cEC63565f616900b513a15fD5f\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"2zmlB6fFjT-cbdqTBfdvet_aUF9pX9QJn72tDc-vVFc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"cwJDUV5Nw5Q2zLlAPlSn6obKTUws33X9rA8D0Nh_JWQ\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Nx_PkbdAq_w_3Ip0PbiXYP6LSvq-RkO75nUUXKKWdbwAVLgmr-Yp1WsM2YGIcM4ZfKkb4BqZA9a4eS7cxz0GvA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x13f0def033c79584470306aea7ecc2155397d75d7e1ac25047b07a37c647f28a0710334b0616cd33d8dfd1992d2a6ada21fd338ddfbac734e5f349a476b854c51c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"2zmlB6fFjT-cbdqTBfdvet_aUF9pX9QJn72tDc-vVFc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"cwJDUV5Nw5Q2zLlAPlSn6obKTUws33X9rA8D0Nh_JWQ\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"-DmTK0TmcBfF8PuJeYA-sw0YQuW46pHJWj3VL6SYBYQ\"}"